title: THIS IS WHY YOU DON'T SUCCEED || EP:144
description:
I'M BACK!!!! And Today is a special day, It's my birthday!!!! And the only gift I want is for you to give YOUR gift to the world! That's why I recorded this episode! Are you tired of being average? Are you sick of just doing the bare minimum? I hope so, because there's a world full of greatness that's available to you! I know this episode is a gut check, but I promise you if will be life changing for it...if you truly understand the message that's being said!
